response.original_title: Kelly Terranova: A Man Named Kelly
response.overview: Despite his name, Kelly Tarranova isn't a beautiful, witty woman, but what he lacks in luscious flowing locks he makes up for in expressive observational humor. In his special, the West Virginia native jokes about budget airlines, getting lost in Ikea, and his hatred of Crocs.
response.title: Kelly Terranova: A Man Named Kelly
